</p><ul style="--pf-line-spacing-xs:10px;--pf-line-spacing-sm:10px;--pf-line-spacing-md:10px;--pf-line-spacing-lg:10px;--pf-text-indent-xs:0px;--pf-text-indent-sm:0px;--pf-text-indent-md:0px;--pf-text-indent-lg:0px" data-pf-type="List2" class="sc-btwLGw cuLvxI pf-86_"><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-gFmZvT eCWkjm pf-87_ pf-text-1"><strong>Leadership commitment</strong> - Leaders must champion innovation and allocate resources to support it.




